  <div>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.58rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-gold);margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Off-Market &amp; Pre-Market Access</p>
    <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-text-primary);line-height:1.6;margin:0;max-width:44ch;">Looking to buy in this area? Register your brief and get early access to properties before they are publicly listed.</p>
  </div>
  <a href="/buyers" style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#191817;background:var(--color-gold);padding:0.6rem 1.2rem;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;transition:background 0.2s;border-radius:8px;">Register your search &rarr;</a>
</div>
